Class AbstractTypesContract

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.florianschoppmann.java.type.AbstractTypesContract
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.testng.ITest

    public final class AbstractTypesContract
extends Object
implements org.testng.ITest
    Contract test for AbstractTypes.

    This class should be instantiated and returned by a TestNG factory method (that is, a method annotated with Factory).

      • testSetup

        public void testSetup()
        Verifies the TypeElement instances in typeElementMap.

        The following is verified:

        • Element.asType() returns "a prototypical type" which is "the element's invocation on the type variables corresponding to its own formal type parameters".
        • type(Class) returns a raw type if the given class object represents a generic type declaration.
        • Passing the raw type returned by type(Class) to AbstractTypes.toString(TypeMirror) yields a string equal to the class's name.
